# 📊 Expense Tracker CLI

A **command-line interface (CLI) application** for managing personal transactions.  
This app allows users to add, update, view, and summarize transactions, as well as search by type, category, user, and more.

---

## ✨ Features

- ➕ Add transactions (income or expense)  
- ✏️ Update existing transactions  
- 🔍 Search transactions by type, user, or ID  
- 📊 Generate transaction summaries by user (total income, expenses, and net balance)  
- 👤 View user information and transactions by user ID or name  

---

